<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Code • Learn to Code</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.7.2/css/all.min.css">
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Poppins:wght@100;200;300;400;500;600;700;800;900&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
  
  <style>
    * {
      padding: 0;
      margin: 0;
      box-sizing: border-box;
    }

    body {
      min-height: 100dvh;
      display: flex;
      justify-content: center;
      align-items: center;
      background-color: rgb(21 23 27);
      font-family: "Poppins", sans-serif;
    }

    .box {
      width: 850px;
      height: 500px;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: row;
      border-radius: 5px;
      box-shadow: 12px 10px 10px 2px rgba(12, 12, 12, 0.58);
      overflow: hidden;
    }

    .content {
      width: 60%;
      height: 100%;
      padding: 30px 80px;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      align-items: start;
      gap: 100px;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgb(113 85 249), rgb(94 64 240));
      color: white;
      border-radius: 5px 0 0 5px;
    }

    .content span {
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: row;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      gap: 15px;
      font-weight: 500;
      cursor: pointer;
    }

    .info {
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: 25px;
    }

    .info p {
      font-size: 40px;
      font-weight: 500;
      max-width: 90%;
    }

    .info button {
      width: 140px;
      height: 50px;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      gap: 10px;
      background-color: rgb(21 23 27);
      color: white;
      border: 0;
      border-radius: 30px;
      cursor: pointer;
      transition-duration: 0.5s;
    }

    .info button:hover {
      background-color: rgb(0, 0, 0);
    }

    .login {
      width: 40%;
      height: 100%;
      padding: 30px;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      align-items: start;
      gap: 20px;
      background-color: rgb(22 24 28);
      color: white;
      border-radius: 0 5px 5px 0;
    }

    .message h3 {
      font-weight: 500;
      font-size: 18px;
    }

    .message p {
      font-size: 11px;
      color: rgb(173, 173, 173);
      line-height: 1.5;
    }

    form {
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: 15px;
    }

    .inputDesign {
      height: 35px;
      width: 285px;
      padding-left: 10px;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      background-color: rgba(12, 12, 12, 0.58);
      border: solid 2px rgba(12, 12, 12, 0.58);
      border-radius: 3px;
    }

    .inputDesign input {
      flex: 1;
      background: none;
      border: none;
      outline: none;
      color: white;
      padding-left: 10px;
      font-size: 14px;
    }

    .inputDesign input::placeholder {
      color: rgb(173, 173, 173);
    }

    .icons {
      width: 18px;
      color: #ffffff;
    }

    .iAgree {
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: row;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 5px;
      font-size: 11px;
    }

    .iAgree input {
      cursor: pointer;
    }

    .btn {
      width: 285px;
      height: 40px;
      color: white;
      background-color: rgb(94, 64, 240);
      border: 0;
      border-radius: 5px;
      cursor: pointer;
      transition-duration: 0.5s;
      font-weight: 500;
    }

    .btn:hover {
      background-color: rgb(70, 33, 255);
    }

    .otherLogins {
      width: 100%;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 15px;
      font-size: 11px;
      text-align: center;
    }

    .socialIcons {
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: row;
      justify-content: center;
      gap: 20px;
    }

    .socialIcons i {
      cursor: pointer;
      transition: 0.3s;
    }

    .socialIcons i:hover {
      transform: scale(1.2);
    }

    /* Responsive */
    @media (max-width: 900px) {
      .box {
        width: 90%;
        max-width: 400px;
        height: auto;
        flex-direction: column;
      }

      .content {
        display: none;
      }

      .login {
        width: 100%;
        border-radius: 5px;
        padding: 40px 20px;
      }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>

  <main class="box">
    <!-- Left Side -->
    <div class="content">
      <span>
        <i class="fa-solid fa-code fa-2x"></i>
        <p>Code</p>
      </span>
      
      <div class="info">
        <p>Learn to code. Interactively. For free.</p>
        <button>
          <span><i class="fa-solid fa-play"></i></span>
          Watch demo
        </button>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Right Side - Login -->
    <div class="login">
      <div class="message">
        <h3>Join over 25 million learners from around the globe</h3>
        <p>Perspiciatis laudantium aperiam eum. Repellat quaerat quae provident iusto esse natus soluta, est ipsum amet molestiae.</p>
      </div>

      <form action="#">
        <span class="inputDesign">
          <svg class="icons" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 512 512">
            <path fill="#ffffff" d="M48 64C21.5 64 0 85.5 0 112c0 15.1 7.1 29.3 19.2 38.4L236.8 313.6c11.4 8.5 27 8.5 38.4 0L492.8 150.4c12.1-9.1 19.2-23.3 19.2-38.4c0-26.5-21.5-48-48-48L48 64zM0 176L0 384c0 35.3 28.7 64 64 64l384 0c35.3 0 64-28.7 64-64l0-208L294.4 339.2c-22.8 17.1-54 17.1-76.8 0L0 176z"/>
          </svg>
          <input type="email" placeholder="email@email.com" required>
        </span>

        <span class="inputDesign">
          <svg class="icons" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 448 512">
            <path fill="#ffffff" d="M144 144l0 48 160 0 0-48c0-44.2-35.8-80-80-80s-80 35.8-80 80zM80 192l0-48C80 64.5 144.5 0 224 0s144 64.5 144 144l0 48 16 0c35.3 0 64 28.7 64 64l0 192c0 35.3-28.7 64-64 64L64 512c-35.3 0-64-28.7-64-64L0 256c0-35.3 28.7-64 64-64l16 0z"/>
          </svg>
          <input type="password" placeholder="*********" required>
        </span>

        <div class="iAgree">
          <input type="checkbox" required>
          <p>I agree to all statements included in 
            <span><a href="#">Terms of Use</a></span>
          </p>
        </div>

        <input class="btn" type="submit" value="Login">
      </form>

      <div class="otherLogins">
        <p>Or continue with these social profile</p>
        <div class="socialIcons">
          <i class="fab fa-google fa-2x"></i>
          <i class="fab fa-facebook fa-2x"></i>
          <i class="fab fa-twitter fa-2x"></i>
          <i class="fab fa-instagram fa-2x"></i>
        </div>
        <p style="color:rgb(74, 98, 255); cursor: pointer;">
          <a href="#">Create an Account</a>
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </main>

  <script>
    // Optional demo functionality
    document.querySelector('form').addEventListener('submit', function(e) {
      e.preventDefault();
      alert('Login Successful! (Demo)');
    });
  </script>
</body>
</html>
